              <s>Please post all bug reports in this thread. General likes/dislikes go in the news discussion thread.</s><BR><BR>All these crazy threads are getting difficult to keep up with, so we're going to do something a little different now.  Please see here: <a href="http://episteme.arstechnica.com/eve/forums/a/tpc/f/51009562/m/499001486931" target="_blank">http://episteme.arstechnica.co...09562/m/499001486931</a><BR><BR>If there's an issue we haven't responded to, or you don't see in that bug system, feel free to submit it.

              

              
              
