              Minor issue:<BR><BR>When switched to the black background, the box in which the "Join the conversation. Discuss this story." link is placed keeps a white background.  Probably just a minor CSS thing, but I guess it could've been intentional (keeping the contents of the box readable).<BR><BR>I'll also second the comment about the Login/Join button not changing when you're already logged in. It should probably change to a logout button or disappear after you log in.<BR><BR>Other than that, I think I like the new layout.  It'll take a little time to get used to and form deeper impressions, but it feels a lot less haphazard/random than the old layout.

              

              
              
